{"tid":453346,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"「我哋未被消滅」Hidden Agenda搬出工廈","createTime":"2017-10-31T05:50:41.000Z","updateTime":"2017-10-31T13:59:06.000Z","uid":25558,"like":4,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"6c5daf471feab49ff399c2734a97626351ae01c9","tid":453346,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-31T05:50:41.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20171031/20199594\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20171031%2F20199594&d=rrT9AL%2Fi%2FwiN14iGQi62JU4boqMkoHyMuoHHSR1H%2BGk%3D&h=32c83aaf\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20171031%2F20199594&h=d4169e4c\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20171031/20199594</a><br />\n<br />\n「我哋未被消滅」Hidden Agenda搬出工廈<br />\n<br />\n港聞   <br />\n         <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n0:00<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】被譽為「Band界紅館」的Hidden Agenda今年5月遭入境處放蛇拉人，引發軒然大波，曾被多次逼遷轉場，今日終正式告別觀塘工廈。<br />\n<br />\nHidden Agenda這次未有後繼場地，暫別觀眾後不知何時東山再起，但負責人阿和稱沒有不捨，「都未完，HA仲喺度，冇咗場地箒！」他強調凝聚到一班支持者是靠對Live House音樂的熱愛，「你唔係話冇咗個場地就代表我哋被消滅」。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20171031/large/31la6p10.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20171031%2Flarge%2F31la6p10.jpg&h=712c64e2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n負責人阿和指希望休息一下，再思考未來方向。<br />\n<br />\n申請牌照處處碰壁<br />\n<br />\nHidden Agenda位於鴻圖道的工廈單位，「準備中」的牌子仍掛在門上，鐵閘半掩，由以住每月「閒閒哋」3、5場演出，經常full house，到今天收拾細軟，音響器材全部打包，門口招牌亦拆下，只等待上貨車入倉。<br />\n<br />\nHidden Agenda於2009年成立以來搬過4次，阿和重溫Hidden Agenda的相片集時指，最有感覺是憶起與受邀樂隊相處的時光，因他除了接洽樂隊到場演出，多數身兼保母，最近一次有深刻印象的是台灣樂隊Hello Nico詹宇庭。阿和第一次見她時，純粹合作夥伴上交流，相處久了，就會對她了解更多，形容詹宇庭「好感性，好有大愛，同時好抑鬱」。<br />\n<br />\n對於政府對待工廈的手法，阿和說，曾經嘗試配合當局，申請相關娛樂場所牌照，但處處碰壁，「係我申請唔到，而唔係我唔申請」，又指曾經請立法會議員譚文豪幫忙，向當局示範逃生安排，但不得要領。<br />\n<br />\n早前施政報告一出，阿和稱「死心」，「講咗（工廈政策）唔會有一part係做演出場地」。他斥政府眼中的藝術空間是「畀一啲藝術家喺一個劏房入面擺張枱，諗嘢嗰啲」。他現時希望休息一下，再思考未來方向。<br />\n<br />\n■記者葉親惠"},{"pid":"10805801d74a1cc6a07e0ada243d40d034ca7184","tid":453346,"uid":87073,"like":3,"dislike":4,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-31T05:51:56.000Z","msg":"旺角行人專用區咪得囉"},{"pid":"a0eaf423e743979ed3b7b30ba1e7666ae07e7e5b","tid":453346,"uid":55488,"like":2,"dislike":11,"score":-9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-31T07:08:33.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"1392c2ffc92288d6cbd78623897dddc66c8f8d28","tid":453346,"uid":28195,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-31T08:01:59.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>mk妹mk仔地方 垃圾</blockquote><br />\n<br />\non9無極限，348咩？"},{"pid":"7a82733c22842fdb6f83b16ff24efcc841933386","tid":453346,"uid":35420,"like":2,"dislike":3,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-31T08:04:18.000Z","msg":"死唔斷氣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ada09204711aeacda02f0a4d9ea35f0612e0012b","tid":453346,"uid":9284,"like":4,"dislike":6,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-31T08:10:53.000Z","msg":"Mk仔又想cap水<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"abd139118eb15e77105daaba069b5843ac033817","tid":453346,"uid":93900,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-31T08:11:33.000Z","msg":"條肥仔無俾人告咩?"},{"pid":"9aa1eec616e731e50cd9b2ffc6a8a62590476b2d","tid":453346,"uid":38671,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-31T08:12:10.000Z","msg":"去旺角行人專用區<br />\n一定好多人支持<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"88268fe1f8a5a9889a12e017feace36ec05f757b","tid":453346,"uid":3649,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-31T10:23:29.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>mk妹mk仔地方 垃圾</blockquote